        <div class="reviewText stacked">
              <span id="reviewTextContainer2849448400" class="readable"
              >
            
<span id="freeTextContainer2133182940488140664">I read this great book many years ago but still can remember that superb atmosphere of long gone glory. Everything is in decay, a once proud aristocrat (the leopard) got old, time overtook him. Here his long life passes in review. And in the end? Well, the book has one of the greatest and most melancholic endings ever. Absolutely recommended. A modern classic!</span>

          </span>
        </div>


